{"tid":2439931,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「你、我、他」呢啲第一二三人稱好少有同音字","createTime":"2021-03-09T14:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T16:48:06.000Z","uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"456efa1f5c175e436dbbaeb25772c735c9b5273c","tid":2439931,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:55:27.000Z","msg":"我頭先查吓中大個粵語網，得勁少同音字，尤其是個「我」字，我真係諗唔到有咩同音字係同「我」一樣<br />\n<br />\n點解會咁呢？<br />\n<br />\n當然<br />\n「你」同音嘅可以係「妳」嗰啲<br />\n「他」同音嘅可以係「她、牠、它」<br />\n不過都係代表第二第三人稱，而唔係其他意思"},{"pid":"070a1b078e1b6503c0f30def46f80bb0e841ccd9","tid":2439931,"uid":251339,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:56:43.000Z","msg":"禾刀吾之"},{"pid":"e305f049b920e4cfd165e48c25b234ce1a29626a","tid":2439931,"uid":370409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:59:26.000Z","msg":"重有兩隻字無同音：<br />\n天<br />\n地<br />\n<br />\n(粵語)"},{"pid":"486547ff27431b745b9a6c96a8e34c9a0b335efb","tid":2439931,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:06:51.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢"},{"pid":"ab30e2c1bf976cba1035a860b04145ce098ff522","tid":2439931,"uid":1845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"李"},{"pid":"6090db05d40335d6914182d3410aa39b0d06fd14","tid":2439931,"uid":387907,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:13:12.000Z","msg":"理<br />\n<br />\n咪同你同音囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保你大<br />\n<br />\n同<br />\n<br />\n保理大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都已經係一樣發音唔同意思啦"},{"pid":"4bbf87da766ebce0891a90e6ec2a7e3d96726425","tid":2439931,"uid":374195,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:16:00.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n樓上講嘅「李」同「理」都係lei<br />\n而「你」係後鼻音nei<br />\n懶音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d725483b312ff6777514f98d463b7c8b4c63d20","tid":2439931,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:20: